Tourist --> UC_BrowsePlaces
Tourist --> UC_ViewPlace
Tourist --> UC_SearchPlaces
Tourist --> UC_FilterCategory
Tourist --> UC_ViewMap
Tourist --> UC_BrowseRestaurants
Tourist --> UC_ViewRestaurant
Tourist --> UC_ViewMenu
Tourist --> UC_MakeReservation
Tourist --> UC_ViewReviews
Tourist --> UC_BrowseStays
Tourist --> UC_ViewStay
Tourist --> UC_ContactOwner
Tourist --> UC_BookAffiliate
Tourist --> UC_BrowseEvents
Tourist --> UC_ViewEvent
Tourist --> UC_RegisterEvent
Tourist --> UC_SetReminder
Tourist --> UC_CancelRegistration
Tourist --> UC_ViewAnalytics
Tourist --> UC_ViewSentiment

' Vendor Use Cases
Vendor --> UC_RegisterVendor
Vendor --> UC_VendorLogin
Vendor --> UC_ManageRestaurant
Vendor --> UC_UpdateMenu
Vendor --> UC_SetHours
Vendor --> UC_ToggleOpen
Vendor --> UC_ManageReservations
Vendor --> UC_CreatePromotion
Vendor --> UC_VendorAnalytics
Vendor --> UC_RespondReviews

' Stay Owner Use Cases
StayOwner --> UC_RegisterStayOwner
StayOwner --> UC_StayLogin
StayOwner --> UC_ManageStay
StayOwner --> UC_UploadImages
